Name
       report_socv_interconnect_variation  -  Reports  the RC variation multi-
       plier data provided in the SOCV files

Syntax
       report_socv_interconnect_variation

       [-help]

       [-delay_corner <string>]

       [-power_domain <string>]

       Reports the RC variation multiplier data provided in the SOCV files.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       -delay_corner <string>
              Specifies the name of the delay corner.

       -power_domain <string>
              Specifies the name of the power domain.

